diminishes at a certain place,

85
00:06:43,135 --> 00:06:46,265
there must be a divergent
flux at the same place.

86
00:06:47,775 --> 00:06:53,040
So the flux j is thus a 
flux of probability density.

87
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:57,840
The validity of Quantum Mechanics is
limited to non relatively velocity,

88
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:02,466
