127
00:09:58,147 --> 00:10:01,470
After all, it moves at the speed of light.

128
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:03,040
The solution is the notion
of your virtual particles,

129
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:08,532
which is central to the action
of forces in field theory.

130
00:10:08,532 --> 00:10:12,920
Virtual particles have all the same
properties as the real ones,

131
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:17,090
except that they can
have a different mass,

132
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:20,900
which can even be negative or
imaginary.

